    "lyrics": {
      "text": "The pow-er of Thy Cross,__ O Lord, in__ truth__ is ver---y great: for it was fixed___ in one___ place, yet doth__ a-vail__ through-out__ the____ world;__ and of__ fish-er--men it made di-vine____ A--pos---tles,__ and of the__ na--tions, Mar---tyrs,__ that__ they might ev------er in-ter-cede__ for our___ sal-va-tion.__"
